Package: animanipulate
Type: Package
Title: Manipulate and animate plots (an extension of gWidgetsManipulate, a
    gWidgets port of RStudio's manipulate package).
Version: 0.5
Date: 2014-02-20
Author: Sebastian Kopf, using existing classes provided by John Verzani's
    gWidgetsManipulate / RStudio's manipulate package
Maintainer: Sebastian Kopf <seb.kopf@gmail.com>
Description: Generate a simple graphical user interface for manipulating and
    animating your plots (inspired by the Mathematica function manipulate and
    implemented as an extension of John Verzani's gWidgetsManipulate package
    which in turn is modeled after RStudio's manipulate package).
Imports:
    gWidgetsManipulate
Depends:
    gWidgetsManipulate
Suggests:
    gWidgetsRGtk2,
    animation
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
